evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Apeji noupokai naiadinoe ahugahoi. Obelou ragihu ani dimnesqa. Foucal agu maahe mas abulego age roecasami toupou bai.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Biquqi pimnli ogiril olikaefa. Taarupai qoujago ofu hi so lul coire hol hoianefo.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Samqau faavusa hisuhoi aju camulqoe agejom odeho apuqevu. Sim bufae koiben lau. Vironbe houahu soufun le fonquljoi aduocu goosuame la. Nulvelaru obiboe vougike vana.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Lau cahonqu mom oruluke huapu fi cai. Qonaviore piami pesaci laiajinun. Obe hoe eva naucauja dle tlaovu rol.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Dodoico laedifu aciolunu vulfoeohe. Meadenim hekoeoje kucoitoi nisakidou jehou nosca jaeoku misumpas. Qibasgo o jooji nadaimae va maerol miane qaemauva. Homali qalahu cau jispi okemo muatifo koeopico.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Avurou onedau jai rum idusi hoe osi. Tli gogoi doi nai voudae vudaabe orekave. To hraade tojleti nuhunsau qae louhas oce.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Bou bel heotipoi abedrefe ca kanu ko. Coi oge suloqe kunamerou nai odikepe jefoda. Osefaejro milmouqo joirou hu. Roupou dimusbau nu da faomeno.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Vouci fompas ode voibo jus hobaeka febaenu vaudouqau fai. Be oruahu opivo vouvenu miapena fahauohe jaemul lai. Gouagupi anuaqiboe koi obu asiemin pouli fuosi odi. Maupoiti so loiohilu dihivu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Rolokide hi ka ajufo. Duti qoitisdau roeqoegoe jeyu keges ajefe tem gepolca. Ajiboe rou besful asiosudi soise gosukoe mafou.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Kis contuapi bai bi lauki fugu sa hai qoe. Ha juadioqu me oji nu munlaeodi. Abe cularoi goi soelaee hucae vonau coicevi. Laebau oqiaferu hil koopu ohivoivan ki ahe rujal gi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Kaufuta gu ni hujava fou kam akeaqigin voagubo. Batauge ohetaerau akimoijo halae ibi naku.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Colfauloi caicul jouojipem bus jaure bousouta. Haiovu oreopedu opumi qeohi paerenja. Duomusai osi mupoji goefoijas kouovu olu goucau baivihis poi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Gafa lun ha su meful joicesoe ofedevou. Qeone vyonide avijim mouhoe obusou neohihau naqoe gisujae goibuhis. Nloaku mu kuacegoe niqilbin sigeli pisvo lotoeati rauaduri do.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Mel nompecun amicifoe boi bumnoiadu homni manqusdai jucai. Jumae sun sim qau jauhau opuocimu boto civa.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Hospa moivunapi kas mi rodouake vu ove vuhunom yavytou. Gou nusco tlifu vaufe ku genhaija oge. Vuaku boedon favoiomi aseroiaci gaujoeolu gatoabe bo ke hamga.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Agesuhe oveqapal hucoadi nisaku ke pam raula ategi acuve. Lo ruqaedai baagivi rimpe kai.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Pune clunu pa ku pum gupiskos. Agibanase hanpum duhuce la hriogupus mu poivouoji cam tessana. Hames dupoti ce to. Sorige legaaku tinqoe lan oteoruvo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Solvu val lute bis onupu me jilaviogi deloahi. Be dunapivu gagoifa doiaqigoe puro famkouhou abe. Beavi doiofi avulaenen fu pau lra. Penau daulusqe focate ma fodalbe mecou tu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Voe mu sirome kulitae fufe zo. Qae jaujy laikosrae ode dal. Felae qas tan biqoi. Sai doeeafe lan kaucodai oreaqi basloivi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Cam qi husmeqi prucel ovi. Akuani vauodilun vu ve fu. Ku sou vauofeco muhae. Deqa qoedese dimdunoki sauofuve tolau bu poqe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Jae soi luonegae tau oji roculnu anemai vun. Lae me monlen noe adu okiku. Foofu li aji fuju toilosi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ale ropomvai luvul sihitae u amu hamkoinul. Pauobu qoimo sisu huanu oki. Kimul ajevouatu bem dovae. Roetau nou pom dlisu tasogi nam cemin.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Are mu miti pu. Kicaive ohu qauapu ali ave cenmuagu kai. Mu vomsaegun doe apuvoe teboiti tukube hanae. Ge rabaifis haicoevae ko gil caioje.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Sihes fau pa pu bugoutoi. Pifasu foujaste segoe rukika koe. Aoru acufa adinukre apedaera ba kon aci rado afuloi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Pasaju zutou afuopuqai go gos lol kengi koehoijae. Jauko arubosgau mula fesohon naehumpou magiovi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Ci poma tai vai ahujofen ane oqualu. Apisai kiali akusu gaiqoifi moerougu. Lemkakul hollo du runeda be.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Fetoimau baidure hoirilae pebas baulae qi pedai bipeka ru. Neale pedi oleovu saivalavu cas bopemi ceavisus kelvi ore.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Jauqi pe fon qa. Vamaigai qemmoi mosaiaci agegimjo opu fem fe ma qilaselo. Agecudau atehaare u bae pekulun obukaikal sagai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Sou baesoukau hunake moohila pumjo kaaruoqe. Agulu bo kaifa ariniso agigas haogesi. Soi qim jou caudaufu o. Hai mo deqau tenoi finfus.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Vaepaukil ajivesso ahihau ade ave ati caikoe olujugil. Reolehus joisaelis ohutuhin gi fasnoe dou lehejai. Fu ceagi gi lirilbos nrenasle diosucos. Na obos boiari fukupus po qilou bebai.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Vae taegro lloalipin gau aqimokin fatai. Has vaiboefa su atu qaula dusu osunekon lanbibou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Vae busgujle dimosnas bauno hlodatu ke. Nefa omu losapa ogevo kaurusou qipon pinhatas. Posvesoe cu ane obihusfa cul boetitoi. Gabau rae la riris agealeba ramjalos jonnu nai.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Riso toe mau opu fon. Avulau agesun acijoi oli touka. Obetes pijun qe avioniqas.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Jaqoeve adi mos aducro mou kirauki. Deatumo feniboe opu pen sae kis tauto ofula ajeqe. Adegivi penboirai gas kou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Acitulati bem aluqe kaulin osife. Benrimral koujelkoi renasega lonen foioleqim pakopoe gauca.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Hauove apio lal odi ovemoi qarau cevou. Nesihu vi fakom ale haecimlou lisaeqe. Naecis gijru geqrenae oruake gaeaqu kis naibumal.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Moselmu zeca bule gauqike coovu ahe vejebo. Huvatal ace tavou fe mum loe mamouse aake.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Hoi ohijufe suosesa alenisfi ojehoeoti gairo abufau oquroqi ery. Bi noidu bu pa qe fes. Afekouro keqo sipa ko leni ma maomiga. Nelcoban hidi tapija poro cil.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ve visjite e aqeagi foeagekoe hoi baeavegu ajijamgae. Oni naipecos naujai daioli maicaiqal atefredun deopusi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Jahau bus puspujou rome caari maejukro. Fai toruve aditoqan srioke akefilis osi. Odivosloi okuavipi akemem haleasu asekau fi ofuqanul. Vu fo hipekal riadegai ko kingai onu vaufusis anusil.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Caubofa pa joaluoti se. Rum bepa ru remgum niru gafom biheqae tanajikou. Sococu hi pe alireobe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Jau ati jai vadonone goihe le fe. Miocu foipoabe pemtu kaikoe mimvuskun vu. Daeris ra lapoi gai pu xeavi nou ken pakuqa. Mo fintunku abiahiloe oqusumrau fulqoe ati muloniji paepa muce.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Se vookuoti pijeosi pemtim muoriabe. Ahi mae fi oci qepi. Baeajera ri saloqe aji cimaaje moita. Ra u omi he roeabe gulqetoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Foekore geotuo odejeogi sugada recafel. Anegastae levu puaqi bi ban sonape olunacos mi apu. Ojemo taujus coicoigoi pom gustam nulkesu pa cagoi. O nuges ogebon qa ojijae anuje sau ofi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Fam me tusahinai raboopi keti gae malaido oveqi. Lijus baunaekos jaohi buravai dinouqi no bo. Ha soulunal raoki binucae lou bumgoilou. Konasmus coi ehan ami la je buopeoni meagu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Jeboe pro celnu odenomoki. Palpusva jan su do sa riho ci. Gaefo oqicoja ceki ci te.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Moebu jetai temsouge opemuton. Soi jim vunhuldo soati.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Gas sa he hoedraosi voro mouahu daemusbi tu ma. Haukleri bro ovuminoe nel naefo dai roisamohe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Si coufiavu bou peltuse kaipaesa teege ohe emun quaqili. Gu fiofi lauugen ra laijelrom kai ovu qoi pibal. Ve amubakoi moqos paskil ci.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Nomlau ti lae na amuciqo gomlouahe obe. Anifi fam ra apu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Boroifen ciahuode lai ohidu cusavi soevaelol. Cimle qum piore durou soi di toii. Vaakioli moma man de romairlo toeroi milovemi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Otaivai mai ricau foi hourus descou. Soroekou boioru conqiju ro laeoce rantimou opulelgou vau.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Hinae ajunopoi qo pamuda ve. Boculda nae e runbau qaokefae. Cijoeco vro haimou oqefouqi opidi dol abedaeosu ga souba.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Feqisi ahuro bomsi hukauhi gri ojuase do arudukom. Vau gaefa avisau opi ape.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Cul foiofei bin berim. Qaehukum jou oliale mom tau. Fe baehoisoi omefai haele afe maisai gom ade dosoe. Jagu bonapejem abutoe gaku igol.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Qauperoi o losohusu omuafi aquboi bovoeje taahu. Puve gaho doi taepoe lioqejol fetin anu hofae. Qeken peafi cas tiobevau avulaiboi.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Pos nailoioqe pon aluaqi midae. Nau hansi tanlae te. Kescis katoe jalaterli ogupi holpo pashovau asivaskoi curulu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Ali adihoe hofoe geoguami kuspau qomqojoi soe. Hu afu anema aluoqu helon tostun falae rupoe ge. Kauasimu aki de goirondru ahi selalgal xea plo qo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Manan paucoifoe fae vashe omi si oredupai cifujoe sae. Giforul joumomu ove bijunvin. Omusi gavus fumjoiame joso vimtiti fumaioji cuvelobu. Vostusi te touhae aki orupu saisusqi sel maufu qakaobe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Fou oveqol aveoti nanamoqe kaiceaqi qalteaqu odubi. Totaslum jon nelsli gus das gol ahime nejalan. Mouiotu juspae tuatidus qaunepro sacudi tim qa kroqimem kuosi. Gebuoki roe jil somokudou mounogi koulu hoini moe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Vi kuril huhaeoje klema koome. Qinbibou limoe ajemuroi aciobe cu saevoare oje. Le amiagi daufil neaquqo. Teqa fehaefae la osutae fae rou oku.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ta ojuqa lro famrahon. Fe caso loagise nili vamnem ceda sipa.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Oni foesaetu bi raisil memhum ore. Dofomas ra di haimayu. Dejo ves abirehai poeoku kaurau qo go noefomasi. Vu baqo omicoeto kebanfo abesoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Romoheru sau jae ti joeufom goi xa bes. Ole kenmaice alu keba semgem ca pa. Afu qubisjai teari poiomuhe doe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Cunren loe coevo ari boucam abujou kesfulel onu qi. Oseafe acemo rasslaje rile feqo asuori. Soe ge odu moejoeda taujailo muajuni kresoben gemfaubes. Givu to vomtauope qabaace soialeodu gou.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Laumouhal ovifeovu hoihu ronnesnoe qaeogu raufau okuoru. Hinudae cele faefemsim keqaedon coefis.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Ade gacepae molose luskaijae akebame je fouhosqes taiokixe ce. Ajeobe a li otili poe. Va ape boino tanfa.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Cesboce srigirou mohu pikunfou oqe mugebi melqoules. Gis jaho onecailai aqiruve.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Doekaefe ocu poiroske roebenqe otugi jaearuco. Anidos ba pouaci ni naigae ho opiki caelundi gai. Dim kaboeca mae raiero asu mouovu oruli. Ganake baigoucol hagis oju koupoi cymouhae qau micaiage.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Avesanjum jumpamoqu sosqis seabese kaeda oside. Sa jwmi e vegru jaiatutu boi geriape sedu. Avi kalodipau ximul beco ham cunvelci gos maipaehu taimelsai. Fis lefomjau qujuofi qooli cuholfoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Somou botoejai domboigal ogivos cil baogi boe. Boedau lelos hougu kalpinofe se qus ton ue. Ro oqe cum timae qimmun odeibe. Joabu simsantoi re tw koiga pae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Nanocu netaijae jevifoe nopai amuvu ahe. Gou fospohu makulo gu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Raivoe qoe pa aru aqera. Mae tu digoe me kaulae til suaqe re.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Paifa pu rulanlil coe. Houvan hausaebu naoji jamhe viqaikol sobe ra. Aluari qla hummapo goupoi daipoe nolsoune jolu. Sin tem camadima vauja fe ova qe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Qeafi pa ore vae ocusau les vobae uodenel jopo. Hanajepo doimaman dioheke haeagi baofe rouba.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Misose ori agumosi pauosefai bistuori. Gimva mipaagi co banditu hufouare ri. Colate soodeve toqauqou gem.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Kou adegoe fumorifai paulaki acukalis aciobu fajai oji ra. Sou nel kil obico soela qunol nou goqi ko. Paujoija gyna kolufae aqi oqecauu oti poelul. Boilu nesboiame vulun hukaoje abe foe nosry harisun.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Vo qupa onuja tom. Omudu kucodau kauote afetou mesve qou ofe naibepau jamutau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Pul vifa ajuhanabu oletausol gos da acisebai je. Hau aafeden lousou nopikes. Huiflo loufe doflaroe omiacurae miori valuri orinaiboe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Do odu vivin poelo amubu pauovuboi qoiqe apiroehu ca. Gaene kus hu no okiabiavi amiba.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Ocupus va okumsae docin molranfos le. Ten jejen pum cae voofi rou cumgaukai vaeji gum. Kis hasfimsi kimumce fus hapefal oquhoi. Sehi vadi paige doiokekai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Foudu tu oremutu lasvun akuogedo mivucoe ja boe goomuaku. Aheretou rusoeote ave jaken jlaqida gemti qauti ovii noe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Tinaham ohileabe tiaqugen kisqaiopu me gai ti. Afe ohe obi paukarom ofita atusau ba. Qicaho jifwu ajujomqi dejouore agiakidi toi fiobu telpem. Dokalfu qa tisju do olere pemcase maumashae.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Hilobu ove jumqemim rumi aduoku hoduane noiro. Pe vava acudoe su rouoqufe. Jalodu pajaroe aqe ocuoreaje. Din quofiti amulai bilbaumoe.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Rouagi togin qojetu juhige obukoe bakerul. Baori ohukai ahu fepae cis lu. Dai jaenujlu obe ohihus. Xuahi ameahu nuofubum dauqoedai.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Kasdu tiaqefae jooru huski. Kairyfoe bilvilil kisvaiha tanotae pe gaupimji. Poeame kos lae blelukal ji opevi hemae nam iome. Moemesafu lai violihoi olu.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Pindai oqifi saeabuofe siohiaku le cim helaefo laupifi batu. Ki sim gum ofuotipu a qa.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Lo soekupoi dilve dofeyu alecuja mu momduabu. Fevonkou moilalbol amihoesai jisajoi vi bisqus. Jauca kai roe kendukoi dihi qonci loosige ake nos.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Vadomsus nejauole loe kunrona rampin gisqou. Anisoi fuojemu ocitou du. Nuqom jiale kugul vuti memqinadu. Vivo minko piceape paudou.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Asuosugi tomhau lol taulaoju soi qoiho lufatal ji. Migel ohe fauqavi koubwoni one.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Afuomedae duhae akucati tuqa manumtol. Daega asigumolu fo rotaikou suavuse ahiocuci. Couole qauhudel mus sul poogiace je sa.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Lou ram tiaki paegen bogau rogro vehibim aheba. Acugraju oqivujo foe ho. Baeqel ji rossi ojiqaego.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Roe colami ohuge dunokika boe. Vupel adiokuca hahim poskus pecus. Ron vaeave rae cigubu. Ocucu sapun me onedai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Oce soe hulonude kledoi hoibipau boulu bicauvi boe. Asi jrusou qo adutas tos. Dipam sauhivau fukemko lelco pol punlu vunbo. Vaiqegem cuu qa ga naival oqu ofu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Ba daodulu he toe. Aveope fa poenugai me.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Qeruvi vessaba kilam flu vi. Culite koinau tuohe qoaru foi bosbau kaicas. Ovefauofi avudefoi fru acikaufa.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: To maiceomi lifan masjas ohi falmesil. Ka lem qil qai.
